When a loan is sanctioned, give your operations officers access to a guided OmniScript to easily collect details about bank accounts and repayment methods. By capturing the repayment schedule details, efficiently manage a loan throughout its lifecycle after it’s disbursed, and ensure that the applicants repay loans according to the agreed-upon repayment terms.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience in Enterprise and Unlimited editions where Digital Lending—India is enabled.

When: Digital Lending—India is available starting on July 16, 2024.
